# Family

**Status:** 🟢 Approved

## Purpose

A Family is the group of people who share everyday life with one or more dogs.

DailyPaws helps each person build their own relationship with the dog while the family grows together.

## What does DailyPaws know?

A Family contains:

- One or more people
- One or more dogs
- Shared goals
- Shared history
- Shared settings

## Person

For each person, DailyPaws may know:

- Name
- Experience with dogs
- Time spent with the dog
- Preferred activities
- Personal goals
- One or more roles

## Roles

Roles describe how a person participates in the dog's life.

Examples:

- Primary Caregiver
- Adventure Buddy
- Play Partner
- Trick Trainer
- Calm Companion
- Walking Partner

A person can have several roles.

Roles may change over time.

## Relationship to other concepts

Each person has one separate Relationship with each dog.

The Relationship is not part of the Family concept and is defined separately.

## Multiple dogs

The Product Model supports several dogs in one family.

The MVP will focus on one dog per family.
